                                 <italic>PRE-OPERATIVE PHASE</italic>
                              </bold></td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td align="left"><italic>Outpatient department of Surgery</italic></td><td align="left">- Scheduling of operation<break/>-Information about the fast track program<break/>-Informed consent</td><td align="left">- Scheduling of operation<break/>-Informed consent</td></tr><tr><td align="left"><italic>Outpatient department of anesthesiology</italic></td><td align="left">- Pre-assessment for risk adjustment<break/>-Discussion focusing on placement of thoracic epidural catheter for management of perioperative analgesia<break/>-Discussion of the essence of the fast track program</td><td align="left">- Pre-assessment for risk adjustment<break/>-Open discussion about different possibilities for management of perioperative analgesia</td></tr><tr><td align="left"><italic>Pre-admission counseling and guided tour on surgical ward</italic></td><td align="left">- Yes</td><td align="left">- No</td></tr><tr><td align="left"><bold>
